---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Less work, more customers" id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    UnAd is the easiest way to connect with your customers through <span class="text-primary">SMS
    marketing</span>.  Say goodbye to complicated marketing tools that require
    hours of training, and hello to UnAd&apos;s user-friendly platform.
    Get started today and watch your business grow!
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="#how-it-works"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="telescope" class="h-8" />
      <span>How it works</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://unad.tech/register"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="rocket" class="h-8" />
      <span>Try it out</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
